{
  "texts": [
    "However, it is conceivable that by then, the ChatGPT models have already undergone improvements, making it sensible to reassess the abstracts at that time.",
    "This study demonstrated the potential application of large language models in scientometrics.",
    "Our study may also stimulate reflection from a broader perspective.",
    "For example, it has been argued that artificial intelligence should play a role in the peer-review process for scientific articles, such as in manuscript pre-screening (Hancock, in press).",
    "In this context, our findings hold important implications."
  ]
